ics and love speaking to people with differing opinions.</p>\r\n<p>FACT 4 - My faith defines much of who I am, and who I want to be.</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"mytabtitle\">VOLUNTEER</h3>\r\n<h4 class=\"mytabsubtitle\">VOLUNTEER WORK</h4>\r\n<p>FRONT END WEB INSTRUCTOR: Worked as an instructor teaching students, ages 11-18, the basic foundations of web design. The curriculum began introducing the students to HTML and CSS, and ending with a final product web page of their own design. </p>\r\n<p>YOUTH MENTOR: Worked with students, ages 11-18, as an assistant instructor of biblical studies. Mentored students to believe in themselves, identify their personal stories,  remain true to their beliefs, love unconditionally, and find value in selfless behavior. </p>", "ABOUT", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "12-revision-v1", "", "", "2016-04-19 03:15:37", "2016-04-19 03:15:37", "", "12", "http://192.168.33.10/isaac-port/2016/04/19/12-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
